177 A.3d 130 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DION L. CROMWELL, A/K/A MALIK CROMWELL, DEON CROMWELL, DION FLEMING, AND DEON FLEMING, AND MALIK CRONWELL, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-443 September Term 2017

079698 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002941-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
